1. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper presents a method for intelligent problem solving using a combination of knowledge-based approach and reinforcement learning, which falls under the domain of AI. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed approach involves the use of reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
3. cs.GT (Game Theory) - The paper applies the proposed approach to playing a strategy game, which is a domain of game theory. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The KB-RL system can be seen as a control system that learns from experience and improves its performance over time. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) - The KB-RL system can be applied to robotics for intelligent decision making and control.
